# auto-api-dotnet — C# client for auto-api.com

- .NET 6+, zero dependencies (System.Net.Http, System.Text.Json only)
- AutoApiClient class implementing IDisposable, 6 async methods
- CancellationToken as last parameter with default value
- Returns typed models (OffersResponse, ChangesResponse) or JsonElement
- PascalCase public members, Async suffix on async methods
- Nullable reference types enabled
- XML doc comments in English
- JsonElement for raw offer data — varies between sources
- ApiException for API errors, AuthException for 401/403

## Key Files

- src/AutoApi/AutoApiClient.cs — main client (6 async methods)
- src/AutoApi/Models.cs — response models
- src/AutoApi/OffersParams.cs — query parameters
- src/AutoApi/Exceptions.cs — exception classes
- src/AutoApi/AutoApi.csproj — project file

## Never

- Add NuGet dependencies
- Use Newtonsoft.Json
- Skip CancellationToken parameter
- Write comments or docs in non-English languages
